  <section id="about" class="section">
    <h2>About CARAVAD</h2>
    <p><strong>Short Bio:</strong> CARAVAD is a creative platform dedicated to exploring the real stories behind the art. Through in-depth shows, interviews, and articles, we highlight the process and people behind the music and creativity that shape our world. Minimalist, soulful, and authentic—that's our lens.</p>
    <p>From in-depth lyric breakdowns to raw behind-the-scenes moments, CARAVAD exists to amplify the voices often left in the background.</p>
